data.title: Dick Cheney and Colin Powell
data.meta_description: Explore the relationship between Defense Secretary Dick Cheney and Chairman of the Joint Chiefs of Staff Colin Powell. They worked closely together in the administration of President George H.W. Bush and largely oversaw Desert Storm, the war to remove Iraqi forces from Kuwait in 1990 to 1991. This resource is part of the Statecraft: The Bush 41 Team collection.
